00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:04,850
have done a mild backtrack with that, and
are saying,

314
00:11:04,850 --> 00:11:06,750
"Oh, only certain people,

315
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:08,540
committing certain actions will be deemed
rioters,

316
00:11:08,540 --> 00:11:12,290
but the event itself, perhaps not".

317
00:11:12,290 --> 00:11:14,500
But, this again is because of

