here.

351
00:12:35,530 --> 00:12:38,350
So, there's a really low tolerance,

352
00:12:38,350 --> 00:12:39,740
and it's really struck me again,

353
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:40,930
despite my years here,

354
00:12:40,930 --> 00:12:44,610
how that can really mobilize people on to
the streets.

